              <h3 class="next-step__title">Encryption Cutover <span class="next-step__done">Up next</span></h3>
              <p class="next-step__text">Complete Phase 4: backfill all plaintext columns to cipher, then drop plaintext columns. The dual-write strategy is already in place — the cutover is a data migration, not a code change.</p>
